OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FI could step down - but not
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fyet, says Pope             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pope Francis has said the time may soon
OL,6, come when he needs to consider stepping
OL,7, down - and would do so if he felt his  
OL,8, health meant that could not serve in   
OL,9, the way he should.                     
OL,11,FHe made the comments at the end of a   
OL,12,Ftrip to Canada - where he apologised to
OL,13,Findigenous people - which involved     
OL,14,Fextensive travel and long days.        
OL,16,FThe 85-year-old pontiff stressed that  
OL,17,Ffor the moment he intends to continue  
OL,18,Fin his duties - and will be guided by  
OL,19,FGod as to when he will step down, if he
OL,20,Fsteps down at all.                     
